text: Claas-Peter Fischer (born 22 February 1968) is a German rower. He competed in the men's coxless four event at the 1996 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1968 births Category:Living people Category:German male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Germany Category:Rowers at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Bremerhaven
